keyFacts: The FBI's New York Field Office, specifically the Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking desk, was actively investigating an Epstein-related complaint as of October 2024.
The complaint originated from a mediator and settlement fund administrator.
The email chain shows coordination between FBI Special Agents to schedule a meeting to discuss the matter.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity related to Jeffrey Epstein years after his death.
